INSTALLATION
------------

1. Create the enrol/authorize directory in your Moodle installation and copy the files and directories in this plugin into it

2. In your Moodle site (as admin) go to Site Administration > Plugins > Enrolments > Manage enrol plugins, and click the eye icon
for the Authorize.Net plugin to open it.

3. Click Settings and fill the configuration form. Save your changes

4. When deploying live, ensure that the "sandbox" setting is disabled in the plugin setting screen.
